title: Next steps.
description:
Hi everyone. 

Once the election is over with I will then push for the Government to take a look at the petition. Please keep sharing, every vote counts. 

Chelsea

title: Over 120,000 signatures since Sunday!
description: Thank you for taking the time out to read my petition, I have only said what we all are thinking! We are doing this together! Please keep sharing and supporting.
